description:
My HoneyDew this week is Retta! The Queen of Duke makes her Dew debut and shares lowlights about her mom being stuck in Liberia during a coup, being the protective friend in college, dating, and a friend’s tragic loss of a child. Retta is one of my favorite people. She can make me laugh no matter what she’s talking about. DUKE DUKE MF’ER! DUKE DUKE!
